The Setup (5 Minutes)
Install: sudo pacman -S keepassxc

Start a "Standard" Agent: Hyprland doesn't start an SSH agent by default. Add this to your ~/.config/hypr/hyprland.conf:

Plaintext
exec-once = ssh-agent -a $XDG_RUNTIME_DIR/ssh-agent.socket
